originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name,
    m.title AS movie_title,
    c.kind AS cast_type,
    co.name AS company_name,
    COUNT(*) AS total_movies
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    aka_title m ON ci.movie_id = m.movie_id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON m.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_name co ON mc.company_id = co.id
JOIN 
    comp_cast_type c ON ci.person_role_id = c.id
WHERE 
    m.production_year BETWEEN 1990 AND 2023
    AND co.country_code = 'USA'
GROUP BY 
    a.name, m.title, c.kind, co.name
ORDER BY 
    total_movies DESC
LIMIT 50

FROM (SELECT "s1"."name" AS "name0", "t1"."title", "comp_cast_type"."kind", "t0"."name", MIN("s1"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("t1"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", MIN("comp_cast_type"."kind") AS "CAST_TYPE", MIN("t0"."name") AS "COMPANY_NAME", COUNT(*) AS "TOTAL_MOVIES"
FROM "comp_cast_type"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "company_name"
WHERE "country_code" = 'USA') AS "t0" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "aka_title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 1990 AND "production_year" <= 2023) AS "t1" INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "t1"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id") ON "t0"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_id" INNER JOIN ("s1" INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "s1"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id") ON "t1"."movie_id" = "cast_info"."movie_id") ON "comp_cast_type"."id" = "cast_info"."person_role_id"
GROUP BY "comp_cast_type"."kind", "t0"."name", "t1"."title", "s1"."name"
ORDER BY 9 DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 50) AS "t4"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "person_id", "movie_id", "person_role_id", "note", "nr_order", "role_id"
FROM "cast_info"

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."ACTOR_NAME", "t4"."ACTOR_NAME") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t4"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t4"."CAST_TYPE", "t4"."COMPANY_NAME", "t4"."TOTAL_MOVIES"
FROM (SELECT "aka_name"."name" AS "name0", "t1"."title", "comp_cast_type"."kind", "t0"."name", MIN("aka_name"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("t1"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", MIN("comp_cast_type"."kind") AS "CAST_TYPE", MIN("t0"."name") AS "COMPANY_NAME", COUNT(*) AS "TOTAL_MOVIES"
FROM "comp_cast_type"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "company_name"
WHERE "country_code" = 'USA') AS "t0" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "aka_title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 1990 AND "production_year" <= 2023) AS "t1" INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "t1"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id") ON "t0"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_id" INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id") ON "t1"."movie_id" = "s1"."movie_id") ON "comp_cast_type"."id" = "s1"."person_role_id"
